{"tid":2430624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參院未獲足夠支持 拜登撤回白宮預算總監提名","createTime":"2021-03-03T05:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T05:39:43.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"131b10fbf8c69cc56b84a456417332f63f0b2cbf","tid":2430624,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"參院未獲足夠支持 拜登撤回白宮預算總監提名<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，由於未能在參議院獲得足夠支持，美國總統拜登撤回對Neera Tanden出任白宮預算總監的提名，成為他上任後建立內閣的首次挫折。<br />\n<br />\nTanden以前透過社交平台攻擊共和黨參議員的往事被「翻舊帳」，但共和黨議員在反對提名此事上亦遭抨擊，被認為是歧視有色人士女性，而他們「縱容」前任總統特朗普任內在社交平台大放厥詞，更顯得現時偽善。"},{"pid":"76b8510fda157646ce6404c175cc1e6f2fe202ac","tid":2430624,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"虛偽敗登注定一事無成啦<br />\n<br />\n共和黨州下星期就會全面復工 經濟up up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敗登聯邦政府= rubbish<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2021/03/02/texas-to-lift-mask-mandate-472690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2F02%2Ftexas-to-lift-mask-mandate-472690&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=3d2069be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/news/2021/03/02/texas-to-lift-mask-mandate-472690</a>"},{"pid":"6cd631a401239b37545f193418569f5d59030b12","tid":2430624,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b8510fda157646ce6404c175cc1e6f2fe202ac","tid":2430624,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"虛偽敗登注定一事無成啦<br />\n<br />\n共和黨州下星期就會全面復工 經濟up up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敗登聯邦政府= rubbish<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2021/03/02/texas-to-lift-mask-mandate-472690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F03%2F02%2Ftexas-to-lift-mask-mandate-472690&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuvYtrFBHe52F